<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195977>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33 – 40. Dorsal and lateral habitus of Peridinetus species. 33 – 34, P. wyandoti, Vara Blanca (Costa Rica); 35 – 36, P. illabes, La Fortuna (Panamá); 37 – 38, P. la etu s, La Selva (Costa Rica); 39 – 40, P. p e n a, La Selva (Costa Rica)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195977/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195978>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41 – 45. Rostrum of species of the Peridinetus sanguinolentus complex, dorsal view. 41, P. l a e t u s, male; 42, P. laetus, female; 43, P. wyandoti, female; 44, P. illabes, female; 45, P. pena, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195978/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

